
Bank Management System



Overview

Welcome to the Bank Management System project! This Java-based application is my first mini project and showcases fundamental Java programming skills.

Features

Account Creation: Create new bank accounts easily.

Deposit/Withdrawal: Add or remove funds from your account.

Balance Inquiry: Check your current account balance.

Account Management: Update and manage your account details.


Getting Started

Prerequisites

Java Development Kit (JDK)

A Java IDE or Text Editor


Installation

1. Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Bank-Management-System.git


2. Navigate to the project directory:

cd Bank-Management-System


3. Compile the Java files:

javac *.java


4. Run the application:

java Main



Usage

Just follow the on-screen prompts to create an account, manage funds, and check your balance.

Contributing

I welcome any suggestions or improvements! Feel free to open an issue or submit a pull request.

Acknowledgments

Thanks for checking out my project! Inspired by basic banking systems to enhance my Java skills.


